3. LLM Integration Code (new files by Arpit Panigrahi)
------------------------------------------------------
   The following files are entirely new additions for this research project:
     Source/llm_search.c    - LLM move search entry point
     Source/llm_parser.c    - UCI move extraction from LLM output
